Global Over The Scope Clips (OTSC) Market Insights
Over The Scope Clips (OTSC) Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Over The Scope Clips (OTSC) Market Overview
The Over The Scope Clips (OTSC) market is projected to experience significant growth, driven by advancements in medical technology and increasing demand for minimally invasive surgeries. The market size is expected to reach USD 1.9 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.7% during the forecast period. This growth is supported by the rising adoption of OTSC in gastrointestinal and endoscopic procedures, where the device is used for tissue closure, hemostasis, and treatment of digestive disorders. Key players are investing in research to enhance product offerings, thus expanding the market reach globally.

